  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion, garlic, and ginger. Cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add cumin powder, coriander powder, garam masala powder, and red chili powder. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add tomato. Cook until the tomato is soft.",
    "Add kidney beans, water, and salt. Bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
